1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:17,510
♪The world keeps changing♪

2
00:00:17,510 --> 00:00:19,980
♪A thousand years pass
in the blink of an eye♪

3
00:00:19,980 --> 00:00:22,160
♪Shoulder to shoulder♪

4
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:24,400
♪We stand above the world♪

5
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:26,590
♪Our identities switch♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:29,320
♪The world turns upside down♪

7
00:00:29,730 --> 00:00:31,730
♪Watch me♪

8
00:00:31,730 --> 00:00:35,320
♪Stir up a storm♪

9
00:00:35,320 --> 00:00:37,610
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

10
00:00:37,610 --> 00:00:40,060
♪Our blood is boiling♪

11
00:00:40,060 --> 00:00:45,290
♪The genius emperor plots
with brilliant strategy♪

12
00:00:45,290 --> 00:00:49,710
♪The slacker general
is unmatched in battle♪

13
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:52,200
♪The business world is in turmoil♪

14
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:54,750
♪The court is rife with intrigue♪

15
00:00:54,750 --> 00:00:59,170
♪We will conquer the world♪

16
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,510
♪There's no escape for the traitors♪

17
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:08,000
=No Way! My Bro Is the Emperor=

18
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:11,160
=Episode 4=

19
00:01:20,810 --> 00:01:22,180
Whoa.

20
00:01:28,570 --> 00:01:29,890
Whoa.

21
00:01:29,890 --> 00:01:31,720
Elite Agent?

22
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:34,520
I've been busy with state affairs,
so I haven't built much.

23
00:01:34,590 --> 00:01:36,400
But I've drawn a lot of designs.

24
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,680
What's this?

25
00:01:45,140 --> 00:01:46,200
Electromagnetic induction.

26
00:01:47,750 --> 00:01:49,220
Using magnets to generate electricity.

27
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:52,950
If we could make electricity in ancient times,
it'd greatly boost productivity

28
00:01:52,950 --> 00:01:54,000
and improve people's lives.

29
00:02:00,390 --> 00:02:02,590
You've even got planes and cannons.

30
00:02:02,970 --> 00:02:04,520
Tanks!

31
00:02:05,440 --> 00:02:06,360
Bro,

32
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:09,160
are you planning to rule the world?

33
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,080
They're just sketches.

34
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:13,720
This era doesn't have the industry.

35
00:02:13,790 --> 00:02:15,240
Everything we can make is here.

36
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,110
I'm not an inventor.

37
00:02:18,320 --> 00:02:19,520
I'm not as smart as you.

38
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,270
But

39
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,030
I have another idea.

40
00:02:24,680 --> 00:02:25,670
I'll take this.

41
00:02:31,040 --> 00:02:31,960
Xiao, look at this.

42
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,070
(Imperial Palace)

43
00:02:34,070 --> 00:02:35,790
The Imperial Palace
and the General's Residence

44
00:02:35,790 --> 00:02:37,710
are separated by one street.

45
00:02:37,710 --> 00:02:39,580
I'm planning to open a Xiaoyao Pavilion

46
00:02:39,580 --> 00:02:41,190
on that street.

47
00:02:41,200 --> 00:02:42,960
You want to use Xiaoyao Pavilion

48
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,040
as our base?

49
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:47,240
You caught on right away.
I've already picked the location.

50
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:49,700
Right here.

51
00:02:50,150 --> 00:02:52,520
We can keep an eye on the palace,

52
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:56,590
and at the same time
monitor the General's Residence.

53
00:02:58,270 --> 00:02:59,920
Sun Beiming's influence

54
00:02:59,920 --> 00:03:01,470
runs deep in the court.

55
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,670
We can't rush this.

56
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:05,520
That's exactly the reason

57
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:09,600
We'll make money

58
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:13,080
while exposing him.

59
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:16,270
With one hand, I'll cut off his money.
With the other, I'll take his army.

60
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:20,000
Those history classes

61
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:21,200
actually paid off.

62
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,960
What are you writing now?

63
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,150
Getting some work done.

64
00:03:31,230 --> 00:03:32,000
Tonight,

65
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:33,110
I'll finish the business plan

66
00:03:33,110 --> 00:03:34,030
for Xiaoyao Pavilion.

67
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:38,920
Forget it.

68
00:03:39,510 --> 00:03:40,950
Relax, please.

69
00:03:40,950 --> 00:03:42,070
Just enjoy tonight.

70
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:43,270
Eat and drink

71
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,480
all we want.

72
00:03:44,790 --> 00:03:45,710
Tomorrow morning,

73
00:03:45,720 --> 00:03:48,200
you and I will leave the palace
to buy the land.

74
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:53,720
(Yunqi Restaurant)

75
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:54,640
Let's go.

76
00:03:55,160 --> 00:03:56,070
There's no need

77
00:03:56,070 --> 00:03:57,040
for Your Majesty

78
00:03:57,040 --> 00:03:58,480
to handle this personally.

79
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,400
Watch me.

80
00:04:03,360 --> 00:04:06,440
(Yunqi Restaurant)

81
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:14,040
I already paid the deposit.
How can you sell it to someone else?

82
00:04:14,040 --> 00:04:16,200
You have no power.

83
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:18,440
They have powerful people backing them.

84
00:04:18,440 --> 00:04:21,520
In the capital, connections are everything.
It's all about who backs you.

85
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:22,920
Cause any more trouble,

86
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:24,640
and I'll throw you in prison.

87
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,200
Just wait.

88
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:29,520
I'll go talk to them.

89
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,440
What's going on?
Didn't you tell them who you are?

90
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:41,240
I did.

91
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:47,920
Every country has its laws.

92
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,230
Every trade has its rules.

93
00:04:49,230 --> 00:04:50,830
According to Jing's Commercial Code,

94
00:04:51,230 --> 00:04:52,670
anyone who breaks a contract

95
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:54,270
is fined fifty taels

96
00:04:54,670 --> 00:04:56,200
and given twenty strokes.

97
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:58,990
Who are you supposed to be?

98
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,390
(Token)

99
00:05:00,390 --> 00:05:02,320
This is the Imperial Dragon Token.

100
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:03,640
I

101
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:06,520
am the Emperor.

102
00:05:16,440 --> 00:05:17,360
See these?

103
00:05:17,400 --> 00:05:19,000
(Token)
This one is from the Imperial Guards.

104
00:05:19,670 --> 00:05:21,080
Court of Judicial Review.

105
00:05:21,320 --> 00:05:22,200
Ministry of Justice.

106
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:23,080
(Imperial Palace Token)

107
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:25,800
Yours is the least convincing.

108
00:05:25,870 --> 00:05:26,870
Throw him out.

109
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:28,310
Wait!

110
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,580
Out of the way!

111
00:05:30,580 --> 00:05:31,500
Out of the way!

112
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:39,430
Sir.

113
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:40,350
This way, please.

114
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:43,600
Lu Ding?

115
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,230
Do you know him?

116
00:05:46,230 --> 00:05:47,190
Vice Minister of War.

117
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,510
One of Sun Beiming's men.

118
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,820
What's he doing here?

119
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:52,430
Don't tell me he's the buyer.

120
00:05:52,640 --> 00:05:54,400
That snake went back on his word.

121
00:05:54,990 --> 00:05:55,660
Pay for it.

122
00:05:55,660 --> 00:05:57,160
Buy the whole street.

123
00:05:58,220 --> 00:05:59,480
I have no money.

124
00:06:01,150 --> 00:06:02,150
The court is corrupt.

125
00:06:02,150 --> 00:06:04,999
I spent everything from my private treasury
helping Hulv open Xiaoyao Pavilion.

126
00:06:06,990 --> 00:06:07,910
Fine.

127
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:10,530
I'll transfer funds
from the frontier headquarters.

128
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,030
There has to be a way.

129
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:15,390
Still, it can't solve our problem here.

130
00:06:22,230 --> 00:06:23,150
Gu Bei.

131
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,510
I have a younger sister.

132
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,870
Before our late father passed,

133
00:06:27,990 --> 00:06:28,840
he entrusted

134
00:06:28,840 --> 00:06:30,720
Princess Xiao Ling with the treasury.

135
00:06:30,990 --> 00:06:32,630
All of Jing's wealth is in her hands.

136
00:06:33,790 --> 00:06:35,040
Marry your sister?

137
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,560
You want me as your brother-in-law?

138
00:06:37,560 --> 00:06:38,550
Trying to pull rank on me?

139
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,750
That's not it.

140
00:06:40,550 --> 00:06:42,750
Sun Beiming has repeatedly petitioned

141
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:45,160
for Xiao Ling to marry
into the Sun family.

142
00:06:45,280 --> 00:06:47,070
If he gets her dowry,

143
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,400
he'll surely raise a private army.

144
00:06:48,870 --> 00:06:49,640
Then neither of us

145
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,720
will make it out alive.

146
00:06:59,520 --> 00:07:01,400
But I've never even met her.

147
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,240
You can't just arrange my marriage.

148
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,640
What's she like?

149
00:07:05,640 --> 00:07:06,600
How's her personality?

150
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,630
My sister

151
00:07:08,960 --> 00:07:09,880
is fine in every way.

152
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,070
It's just that

153
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,400
she's quite into some arts.

154
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:28,920
(Xiao Ling'er, Princess of Jing)

155
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,920
Just a little more.

156
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:43,480
Couldn't you have held on a bit longer?

157
00:07:45,990 --> 00:07:47,510
Your standards are too high.

158
00:07:47,670 --> 00:07:49,870
This painting is perfect.

159
00:07:51,550 --> 00:07:52,630
Nan.

160
00:07:53,277 --> 00:07:55,040
It's been so long since you visited.

161
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,310
I'm here today

162
00:07:56,310 --> 00:07:59,240
to congratulate you on your engagement.

163
00:07:59,870 --> 00:08:01,240
My engagement?

164
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,430
How come I know nothing about it?

165
00:08:03,430 --> 00:08:04,460
His Majesty intends

166
00:08:04,460 --> 00:08:06,190
to marry you to my brother,

167
00:08:06,190 --> 00:08:07,160
Gu Bei.

168
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,960
Gu Bei?

169
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,070
The one who

170
00:08:12,350 --> 00:08:13,640
caused a scene

171
00:08:13,640 --> 00:08:15,160
at court?

172
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,870
That frontier commander?

173
00:08:21,550 --> 00:08:23,310
I'm not marrying

174
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:25,870
some brute
who only knows how to wield a sword.

175
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:28,110
Where's my brother?

176
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,600
Eunuch Xu said

177
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,480
His Majesty and my brother

178
00:08:31,480 --> 00:08:32,870
went incognito to inspect the city.

179
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:34,790
It's dangerous outside!

180
00:08:34,790 --> 00:08:35,790
My brother has never

181
00:08:35,790 --> 00:08:36,790
done anything

182
00:08:36,790 --> 00:08:37,960
so reckless before.

183
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:39,720
It must be Gu Bei

184
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:41,670
who influenced him.

185
00:08:41,670 --> 00:08:42,590
Right?

186
00:08:48,230 --> 00:08:49,550
I'm going to find him.

187
00:08:49,750 --> 00:08:51,110
Ling'er.

188
00:08:51,310 --> 00:08:52,230
Ling'er.

189
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,440
Take this to Lu Ding.

190
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,480
I'm sure he'll come.

191
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,640
Where is he?

192
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:16,710
Over there.

193
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,400
Tell me.

194
00:09:26,840 --> 00:09:27,960
Did only the two of them come?

195
00:09:27,960 --> 00:09:29,280
No guards?

196
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:30,190
Yes, sir.

197
00:09:30,190 --> 00:09:31,600
It's just the two of them.

198
00:09:39,310 --> 00:09:41,160
Guards! Someone's impersonating the Emperor!

199
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:41,880
Seize him!

200
00:09:41,880 --> 00:09:42,800
Now!

201
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,030
(Xiao Ce,)

202
00:09:46,470 --> 00:09:50,360
(I couldn't touch you inside the palace.
Now you've come right to my doorstep.)

203
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:51,680
(I might as well)

204
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,520
(have you killed.)

205
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,560
You dare

206
00:09:54,830 --> 00:09:57,110
commit treason?

207
00:10:00,110 --> 00:10:01,970
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

208
00:10:01,970 --> 00:10:04,350
♪Our spirit soars to the skies♪

209
00:10:04,350 --> 00:10:09,790
♪The brainy emperor plots the strategy♪

210
00:10:09,790 --> 00:10:14,170
♪The slacker general leads the charge♪

211
00:10:14,170 --> 00:10:16,580
♪Swords clash and warhorses thunder♪

212
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:19,120
♪Let the history judge our deeds♪

213
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:24,790
♪Our brotherhood is priceless♪

214
00:10:24,790 --> 00:10:30,350
♪Peace across the land, carefree at last♪

215
00:10:34,640 --> 00:10:36,700
♪Funny moments never stop♪

216
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,510
♪Silly blunders never cease♪

217
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:43,880
♪Yet through every up and down♪

218
00:10:43,880 --> 00:10:45,850
♪We create miracles♪

219
00:10:46,150 --> 00:10:48,610
♪From naive youths♪

220
00:10:48,870 --> 00:10:51,350
♪To legendary heroes♪

221
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:53,300
♪This journey♪

222
00:10:53,300 --> 00:10:57,310
♪Is one we'll be proud of♪

223
00:10:57,310 --> 00:10:59,860
♪Let's time-travel, bro♪

224
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:05,200
♪Let's create♪

225
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:15,160
♪A legend of our own♪

